              <span id="reviewTextContainer2028088333" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer9617807057591279609">Really enjoyed this book, it had me hooked from the beginning.<br/><br/>Cilla is a radio DJ who does the late night show, during one of her request section she gets a caller who makes threats against her and her life. Trying to be brave and play it off, Cilla has no choice but to contact the police when the caller continues to ring into the show every night. In walks a cop Boyde, a typical alpha male who wants to protect Cilla her stalker whilst keeping her for himself.<br/><br/></span>

          </span>
        </div>


