        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2821982036" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16492967455903236176">It&apos;s been a while since I&apos;ve read a Nora Roberts novel. This was a pretty mild read. Yes some of it was a bit formulaic but over all it wasn&apos;t a bad light romantic suspense. I didn&apos;t like the way the scenes with the antagonist was handled in the end. It felt a little rushed but over all I enjoyed the book.</span>
  <span id="freeText16492967455903236176" style="display:none">It's been a while since I've read a Nora Roberts novel. This was a pretty mild read. Yes some of it was a bit formulaic but over all it wasn't a bad light romantic suspense. I didn't like the way the scenes with the antagonist was handled in the end. It felt a little rushed but over all I enjoyed the book.</span>
